snippet.title: Warner Bros Latest Statement About Keeping Amber Heard As Mera | Flixet
snippet.description:
In today's video, we are going to share Warner Bros's Latest Statement about the role of mera in Aquaman 2. 

SUBSCRIBE FOR MORE : http://bit.ly/32rc7vI
______________________________________________

Despite a growing fan movement to remove Amber Heard from Aquaman 2, Warner Bros. cannot fire her or ask her to resign, as they did in the case of Johnny Depp and Fantastic Beasts 3. This is largely due to how various legal issues are handled differently in different countries; a point that has only served to pour gasoline on the fire of an already explosive situation. 

Music In This Video : 

Track: Odessa — LiQWYD & Scandinavianz
Music provided by Audio Library Plus
Watch: https://youtu.be/jNy-Dp3lgcg
